metadata.description:
I created Piso 23 inspired on Lo-fi music; the keys, pads, synths and vocal chops are sounds commonly used in this music genre, so i decide to experiment and combine it with some reggaetón drums. Piso 23 is the result.

The remix is a collaboration with Xcelencia; an artist and friend who has believed in me since my first day on web3. Enjoy the remix.

Performed by Alex Paul and Xcelencia
Produced by Alex Paul
